<p>The one? The clip then cuts to what appears to be then end of Locky's date with Bec, where he confesses: 'Yeah, Bec could literally be the one'</p>

<p>At the beginning of the episode, host Osher reveals to the ladies that an intruder will be joining the race for Locky's heart during a final zoom meeting.</p>

<p>The news of more competition for the adventurous heartthrob leaves the ladies in utter shock.  </p>

<p>The Bachelor continues Wednesday from 7:30pm on Channel 10 </p>

